  "slug": "what-new-income-streams-have-appeared-journal",
  "title": "What new income streams have appeared",
  "subtitle": "A journal set for taking stock of income that arrived and building evidence of financial growth.",
  "excerpt": "A journal prompt set from Day 49 of the MONEY program. The prompts ask you to name every income stream from the current period, including ones you've been minimising.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from Day 49 of The Money Journal: 12 Weeks to Peace, Freedom and Overflow (Rebecca J Page, 2025).",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A journal set from Day 49 of the MONEY program. The purpose is to name what arrived financially over a recent period, and to recognise streams that were dismissed or minimised at the time.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to journalling as a practice? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "journal prompts as practice",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/journal-prompts-as-practice"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Warm-up",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Over the last month, what income arrived?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "List all of it. Main income, side income, unexpected income, any paid work of any kind. Don't filter by size.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Which of those streams did you barely notice when the money arrived?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Name them. Write what you told yourself about why they didn't count.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Closer in",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What new income streams have appeared in the last six months that weren't present before?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write each one. Include things you've dismissed as too small or too inconsistent to count.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What one income stream are you most grateful for right now?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write specifically why. The amount, the source, what it made possible.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What would you need to believe about money for steady, small streams to feel like genuine progress?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write it as a statement you could carry into next week.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where this practice comes from",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Adapted from Day 49 of The Money Journal: 12 Weeks to Peace, Freedom and Overflow (Rebecca J Page, 2025).",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
